                <note rend="inline" type="source">890D.01/5–3145: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Truman</persName> to the
                        British Prime Minister</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Churchill</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-05-31">31 May,
                            1945</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>50. The telegram to General de Gaulle proposed in your number 59<note n="79"
                        xml:id="d1090fn79">May 30, <ref target="#pg_1116">p. 1116</ref>.</note>
                    meets with my approval.</p>
                <closer>[<signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Harry</hi> S <hi rend="smallcaps">Truman</hi>
                    </signed>]</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
